Scathing details have emerged on how fired Babes Wodumo’s manager, Sanele Dlokolo, obtained several s-ex tapes featuring Babes Wodumo and her lover, Mampintsha. A case was opened against Sanele after a hidden camera was discovered in Babes Wodumo’s hotel room and Sanele was apprehended with 7 different s_ex tapes in his laptop which were taken between the 3rd of July and 8th of October 2016. Further investigations revealed that Sanele had tried to blackmail Babes Wodumo and Mampintsha by asking them for money or he would leak the tapes. When LiveMonitor contacted the police constable handling the matter he said he was not at liberty to reveal any sensitive information that could jeopardize investigations but another source close to the couple said they got a tip from one of Babes Wodumo’s dancer’s who then tipped off Mampintsha, Babes Wodumo is said to be dejected and really stressed by the s_ex tapes that she has had to attend counselling. “Her father is a pastor so you can understand why this is really affecting her,” the source said. Both Babes and Mampintsha, were not available for comment Source : LiveMonitor ! These content links are provided by Content.ad. Both Content.ad and the web site upon which the links are displayed may receive compensation when readers click on these links. Some of the content you are redirected to may be sponsored content. View our privacy policy here. To learn how you can use Content.ad to drive visitors to your content or add this service to your site, please contact us at info@content.ad. Family-Friendly Content Only recommend family-friendly content Website owners select the type of content that appears in our units. However, if you would like to ensure that Content.ad always displays family-friendly content on this device, regardless of what site you are on, check the option below. Learn More 0 comments